[center][b]Auto-Favourites[/b][/center]
[b]This tut opens the 'add to favourites' window automaticly if the page is loaded :D[/b]
[i]Change the [tt]<body>[/tt] tag by this as an onloader:[/i]
[code]<body onLoad="if(document.all) window.external.AddFavorite(window.document.location,window.document.title)">[/code]
